[[File:AnsonTraskTehNoob-SWL4.jpg|thumb|right|Anson Trask is called a noob by the other stormtroopers of Joker Squad on [[Yinchorr/Legends|Yinchorr]].]]
A '''noob''', or '''newbie''', was a [[Gungan/Legends|Gungan]] word used to describe any newcomers who entered their [[Swamp/Legends|swamps]]. The word had since spread across [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]], describing anyone new to an area or a job as a "newbie."<ref name="Manual">{{GalaxiesAED}} ''Adventure Manual''</ref>

==Behind the scenes==
In Internet culture, ''newb'', [[Wikipedia:Newbie|''noob'']], and ''n00b'' are generally derogatory slang terms for a ''newbie'' (an inexperienced newcomer) who is rude, ignorant or incompetent in an online game, forum, or other means of interaction.

